{
  "texts": [
    "This may lead to inaccurate multi-step predictions from the true dynamics.",
    "• State abstraction model: (z t, a t) → (z t+1, r t).",
    "This model learns the mapping between the observation and the compact latent representation, similar to auto-encoder (Rumelhart et al. 1985).",
    "State abstraction can reduce computational effort, and simplify planning and policy updating.",
    "• Temporal/action abstration model: (s t, u t) → (s t+l, ∑ t+l-1 t r t)."
  ]
}